item.title: kiosk compact substation
item.description: General YBW series prefabricated compact transformer is a kind of set of equipment which assembles the MV switch apparatus, prefabricated compact transformer, LV distribution equipment together according to fixed connection scheme. This series substation is suitable for neighborhood unit, hotel, large-scale work site and high building that the voltage is 11kV /15kV/17.5kV/34.5kV prefabricated compact transformer, the frequency is 50/60Hz and the prefabricated compact transformer capacity is under 2500kVA Standards: IEC60076,IEC1330, ANSI/IEEE C57.
